			<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="365" y="=" x="55" type="question"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#0000FF" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Some experts <B>estimate</B> that up to 1.5 billion people speak some English nowadays.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT><TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">There [5] to be up to 1.5 billion people who speak some English nowadays.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
