			<paragraph indent="0" tabs="19" style="normal" height="0" width="49" y="+16" x="7"><![CDATA[<tab><B>#q</B>]]></paragraph>
			<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="365" y="=" x="55" type="question"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#0000FF" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Many people <B>consider</B> the biggest problem to be which language to choose as an international language.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT><TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">The biggest problem [6] to be which language to choose as an international language.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
