			<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="365" y="=" x="55" type="question"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#0000FF" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Many people <B>feel </B>that if an international language was imposed on people, there would be a strong reaction against it.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT><TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">It [7] that if an international language was imposed on people, there would be a strong reaction against it.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
