			<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="365" y="=" x="55" type="question"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#0000FF" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">People generally <B>agree</B> that artificial languages such as Esperanto are not the solution to the problem.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT><TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">It [9] that artificial languages such as Esperanto are not the solution to the problem.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
